```plantuml
@startuml dwt0317_Search_Adserver

actor User
participant "Search Interface" as SearchInterface
participant "ESServlet" as ESServlet
participant "BingServlet" as BingServlet
participant "AdRetrieval" as AdRetrieval
participant "RewritingHandler" as RewritingHandler
participant "Thrift Ad Ranking Service" as ThriftAdRanking
participant "ESHandler" as ESHandler
participant "DBPool" as DBPool
participant "Log4j" as Log4j

User -> SearchInterface: Enter Search Query
SearchInterface -> ESServlet: Process Query
ESServlet -> RewritingHandler: Rewrite Query
RewritingHandler -> QueryRewritingService: Rewrite Query
QueryRewritingService --> RewritingHandler: Rewritten Query
RewritingHandler --> ESServlet: Rewritten Query

alt Use Elasticsearch
    ESServlet -> ESHandler: Retrieve Ads
    ESHandler --> ESServlet: Ads
else Use Bing API
    SearchInterface -> BingServlet: Process Query
    BingServlet -> ExternalBingAPI: Retrieve Results
    ExternalBingAPI --> BingServlet: Search Results
    BingServlet --> SearchInterface: Search Results
end

ESServlet -> AdRetrieval: Retrieve Ads
AdRetrieval -> DBPool: Fetch Ad Info
DBPool --> AdRetrieval: Ad Info

AdRetrieval -> ThriftAdRanking: Rank Ads
ThriftAdRanking --> AdRetrieval: Ranked Ads

AdRetrieval -> SearchInterface: Deliver Ads
SearchInterface -> Log4j: Log User Interaction

@enduml
```